  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b87\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The day is not far when people will take to the streets in Pakistan like in Sri Lanka - Imran Khan",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Prime Minister Imran Khan has said that a moment like Sri Lanka will happen in Pakistan.",
        "He said that the day is not far when people will fill the streets for Haqqi Azadi in Pakistan like in Sri Lanka.",
        "He stated this on Twitter and mentioned that the Asivzardari Sharif family mafia has weakened the country in political economy in three months.",
        "Imran Khan questioned that they have saved the wealth accumulated for 30 years after looting Pakistan, how long will the government agencies allow this?"
      ],
